00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:34.740
=Twin Fates=

00:00:34.935 --> 00:00:38.335
=Episode 5=
(Three Golden Feathers)

00:00:38.360 --> 00:00:39.800
If you don't believe me

00:00:40.080 --> 00:00:41.440
and insist on seeing the scar,

00:00:42.520 --> 00:00:44.040
we'll do it right here.

00:01:06.920 --> 00:01:07.720
Is that enough?

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:10.040
How could it be?

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:11.000
You!

00:01:13.320 --> 00:01:15.920
(You want to pin the crime of treason
on me in front of His Majesty?)

00:01:16.760 --> 00:01:18.920
(Then I'll make you dig your own grave)

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:19.920
(before everyone.)

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:22.880
Yuanying, have you found that scar?

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.120
Please

00:01:26.720 --> 00:01:28.440
look carefully.

00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:38.520
If I'm using her identity,

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:40.720
I should go all out.

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:16.480
(What you see)

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:18.640
(is what I want you to see.)

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:22.360
(All the effort
you put up on this stage.)

00:02:23.320 --> 00:02:25.160
(What a shame.
I still caught the attention.)

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:31.480
Your Majesty

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:33.520
and Father have no doubts,

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:36.120
do you?

00:02:37.080 --> 00:02:38.440
I never had any doubt.

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:05.040
Who is he?

00:03:06.600 --> 00:03:09.520
Your Majesty, he's my guard.

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:17.280
Qingci's identity

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:20.360
must not be questioned anymore.

00:03:21.600 --> 00:03:22.400
Come.

00:03:22.960 --> 00:03:24.880
Take Miss Qingci downstairs to change.

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:26.160
Don't catch a cold.

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:43.960
(Guard?)

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:49.160
Feng.

00:03:49.920 --> 00:03:51.680
What has gone into you, Chi Yu?

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:55.040
You tied me up last night.

00:03:56.320 --> 00:03:58.120
I... I...

00:03:58.280 --> 00:04:00.160
I had no choice.

00:04:06.880 --> 00:04:07.760
Actually,

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:09.600
I...

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.760
Chi... Chi Yu.

00:04:15.440 --> 00:04:16.840
Chi Yu.

00:04:26.840 --> 00:04:28.920
I'm sorry, Lord Divine Beast.

00:05:26.780 --> 00:05:28.440
Didn't you say you were hit
by the bewitching spell?

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.920
This is clearly Ji Yuanying's plot.

00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:32.640
If I hadn't tied you up,

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:34.960
she would've accused us

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:36.360
of being in the same room
when she found us.

00:05:37.200 --> 00:05:38.240
Besides,

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.320
it was raining last night.

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:41.560
The rain could calm you.

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:01.440
It's nothing. Just a flesh wound.

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:04.160
It not only weakens
Ji Yuanying's influence,

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:05.400
wins the pity

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:06.920
of Lord Yi and His Majesty,

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:08.760
but also proves my identity
as Ji Qingci.

00:06:09.080 --> 00:06:09.920
A good deal.

00:06:12.040 --> 00:06:13.480
You're scheming indeed.

00:06:14.200 --> 00:06:15.960
You do everything to reach your goal.

00:06:16.280 --> 00:06:17.800
Ji Yuanying is vicious.

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:19.320
I must plan every step

00:06:19.640 --> 00:06:21.400
to secure my footing soon

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:22.920
and gather evidence

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:25.760
to clear the Mu family's name.

00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:31.840
Also,

00:06:33.920 --> 00:06:36.320
I could hand myself over to you
in one piece sooner.

00:06:37.240 --> 00:06:38.000
You're arrogant.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.760
How will you ensure your own safety?

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:42.680
Well...

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:00.960
How long will you keep hugging me?

00:07:05.748 --> 00:07:07.720
I... I didn't mean it.

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:13.720
Stop sneezing.

00:07:14.960 --> 00:07:15.760
It's not that.

00:07:15.760 --> 00:07:17.240
I couldn't help myself.

00:07:24.480 --> 00:07:25.760
I just saw

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:27.680
Ji Qingci sneaking out

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:29.000
through the backyard.

00:07:29.760 --> 00:07:31.480
She went out alone?

00:07:34.840 --> 00:07:37.600
Seems like my dear sister

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:39.560
has many secrets.

00:07:40.760 --> 00:07:42.840
Today is the Ghost Festival.

00:07:43.400 --> 00:07:45.320
Isn't she afraid of

00:07:45.320 --> 00:07:46.880
running into evil spirits outside?

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.800
If that happens,

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:53.800
she may never return.

00:08:31.960 --> 00:08:32.560
(Father,)

00:08:33.440 --> 00:08:34.160
(Mother,)

00:08:34.920 --> 00:08:36.760
(I will clear the Mu family's name)

00:08:37.280 --> 00:08:39.200
(using Ji Qingci's identity.)

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:41.400
Xue.

00:08:44.040 --> 00:08:44.840
Xue.

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:47.960
Xue, you're back.

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:51.480
Father.

00:09:00.400 --> 00:09:01.120
Father.

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:01.600
Come here.

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:04.760
Xue, let me hold you.

00:09:12.520 --> 00:09:14.280
Father, come chase me.

00:09:14.280 --> 00:09:15.480
Careful, Xue.

00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:16.680
Don't fall.

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:18.240
Slow down.

00:09:18.400 --> 00:09:19.400
Come on.

00:09:19.400 --> 00:09:20.800
I can't catch up with you.

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:22.640
Xue, come here.

00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:24.480
I made you a new pair of shoes.

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:25.280
Try them on.

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:27.240
Come on.

00:09:57.800 --> 00:09:59.160
Father, Mother,

00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:01.960
come out.

00:10:03.080 --> 00:10:05.000
I miss you.

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.800
Father, Mother,

00:10:11.801 --> 00:10:14.521
I'll definitely clear your name.

00:10:36.760 --> 00:10:38.280
(The sky lanterns are bright.)

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:40.960
(Father and Mother)

00:10:40.960 --> 00:10:42.480
must be watching me from above.

00:11:44.840 --> 00:11:46.680
No one can threaten

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:48.840
my position as heiress anymore.

00:11:50.720 --> 00:11:52.840
The poisoned needle
isn't from the mortal realm.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:54.200
Once pierced,

00:11:55.840 --> 00:11:57.240
the victim won't last
more than three days.

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:16.000
Don't move,

00:12:16.760 --> 00:12:17.880
or the poison will spread faster.

00:12:42.880 --> 00:12:43.680
This is bad.

00:12:44.640 --> 00:12:45.480
There's no time.

00:12:51.720 --> 00:12:54.280
=Twin Fates=
=End of Episode 5=

00:12:55.520 --> 00:12:59.440
♪In a world of sorrows,
every encounter is fleeting♪

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:05.320
♪Life is short
but slumber is long on Penglai Island♪

00:13:07.320 --> 00:13:11.840
♪In dreams, mountains and flowers are
as beautiful as jade♪

00:13:13.080 --> 00:13:17.120
♪All I ever wish for
is an old friend's return♪

00:13:19.080 --> 00:13:22.920
♪Majestic as a soaring dragon,
veiling the sun with drifting clouds♪

00:13:24.920 --> 00:13:28.680
♪Graceful as a flying swan goose,
breaking through snow and peril♪

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:35.640
♪Twenty years forsaken,
I lived the life of an outlaw♪

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:40.320
♪On the Ximo River,
who was left behind?♪

00:13:40.800 --> 00:13:46.680
♪Bit by bit,
reality shatters my only hope♪

00:13:47.200 --> 00:13:52.520
♪Layer by layer, cold blades roll up
the light I once glimpsed in secret♪

00:13:52.520 --> 00:13:55.320
♪Letters have long since yellowed♪

00:13:55.680 --> 00:13:59.080
♪Leaving only two lonely lines♪

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:04.440
♪Even the old yard is covered
with frost♪

00:14:04.440 --> 00:14:09.360
♪Pair after pair,
swallows draw my envious gaze♪

00:14:10.440 --> 00:14:16.120
♪Scene after scene,
in dreams I cannot reach♪

00:14:16.120 --> 00:14:18.720
♪While you rest beneath the earth♪

00:14:18.720 --> 00:14:22.320
♪My love lingers in this frosty world♪

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:30.960
♪How are you now?♪